Package weloveclouds.server.services.utils

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IReplicationTransferer
    Common methods for those classes which can replicate the requests on replicas.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractReplicationRequest<T,E extends AbstractReplicationRequest.Builder<T,E>>
    An abstract class which represents a replication request that shall be executed on the replicas.
    AbstractReplicationRequest.Builder<T,E extends AbstractReplicationRequest.Builder<T,E>>
    Builder pattern for creating a AbstractReplicationRequest instance.
    DeleteReplicationRequest
    Represents a DELETE replication request that shall be executed on the replicas.
    DeleteReplicationRequest.Builder
    Builder pattern for creating a DeleteReplicationRequest instance.
    PutReplicationRequest
    Represents a PUT replication request that shall be executed on the replicas.
    PutReplicationRequest.Builder
    Builder pattern for creating a PutReplicationRequest instance.
    ReplicationTransferer
    An implementation of a IReplicationTransferer which can replicate the requests on replicas.
    ReplicationTransferer.Builder
    Builder pattern for creating a ReplicationTransferer instance.
    ReplicationTransfererFactory
    A factory to create ReplicationTransferer instances.
